column1: SPF Power on the Mountain Results
We would like to thank Michael Howard and Peak Fitness for hosting this event for the SPF. We
Also would like to thank Jim Pickett, Brent Pickett, and Michael Howard for the Great job of Judging
And keeping everything running smoothly on the platform, also thanks goes out the Spotters/loaders
And to every single person that helped make this a perfect day.
There is a correction on the Raw Bench Press, Brian George was given 2nd. place at the meet, which
Was wrong, he got 1st. place in his weight class. I made a mistake at the meet and caught while fixing
This report. Some have him call or e-mail so I can send him the right name tag for his award.
